EN: He is willing to sacrifice everything for his career.

ZH: 她愿意与你分享她的秘密。
EN: She is willing to share her secret with you.

ZH: 我愿意陪你去医院做检查。
EN: I am willing to accompany you to the hospital for a check-up.

